Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ không bỏ cuộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhanh qá.
